### 13. Create Product with Validation Error (Missing Required Fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "TEST",
  "name": "AB"
}

### 14. Create Product with Duplicate SKU
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "LAPTOP-001",
  "name": "Another Laptop",
  "price": 999.99,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### 15. Sort Products by Price (Ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort=price&order=asc

### 16. Sort Products by Created Date (Descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort=created_at&order=desc

### 17. Search by Category Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/products?category=Books

### 18. Complex Search Query
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/products?q=gaming&category=Electronics&status=active&min_price=1000&max_price=3000&sort=price&order=desc&page=1&per_page=20

